                    "text": "The verify_zip tool just returned. Check the 'serviced' field:\n\n- If serviced=true: Say the message from the tool (e.g. 'Great, we service the [city] area!'). Then ask: 'How can I help you today? Are you looking to book a new service or calling about a previous appointment?' Transition to Sales_State or Support_State based on their answer.\n- If serviced=false: Say the message from the tool (e.g. 'Unfortunately we don't currently service [city]...'). Then say: 'We cover the greater Charlotte, NC metro area. If you believe this is a mistake, please feel free to call us back.' Then transition to End Call."
